{
  "stem": "27509.9",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You can't-- you can't think too hard, too long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was desperate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I turned around to him, and I said, I can only do one thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I've got personal friends in all the universities, at Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I gave him names of professors in law and in so on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I gave him names of professors at Monash.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, it occurred to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wait a minute, I said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is a professor right here at La Trobe who knows me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "His name is Professor [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he said.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know Professor [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said yes, I know Professor [NON-ENGLISH], and Professor [NON-ENGLISH] knows me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you care to inquire about me from Professor [NON-ENGLISH], he'll be able to give you some sort of a opinion about me, or my capacity to study, or whatever you want to know from him.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, that's perfectly all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I won't have to ring him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If you know Professor [NON-ENGLISH], Professor [NON-ENGLISH] knows you, you are in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You are in, and wrote a note for acceptance, and then turned around to me and says, tell me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "With all the connections-- and I'm not mentioning all those names of the other professors, because I don't want to just mention names-- why didn't you use all those connections?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, it never occurred to me that I ought to get into a university by using connections of people who happen to know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to get into university on the merits of my own ability or otherwise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, after one year, I finished up with-- I took three subjects there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every one of them asked me to do an honorary-- a honors course in his particular subject.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
